{"tid":1659470,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"建議開post 增加 \"不上熱門\" (opt out) 功能","createTime":"2019-10-17T03:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T23:39:30.000Z","uid":133727,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"db845ce6cefa3fa61fd895bfae35b570fa807eba","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"開post 時樓主可以選擇&quot;不上熱門&quot; (opt out )<br />\n咁個無論幾多人入個post /留言, 個post 都唔會上到熱門<br />\n<br />\n哩個功能係方便啲日常post, 例如啲無聊, 搞笑, 非政治, 非主線post <br />\n可以正常討論又唔會阻到主線post<br />\n例如&quot;有冇人屋企啲壁虎好撚廢&quot;, &quot;雪莉死左？&quot;<br />\n哩啲post 比人罵係廢post 阻住主線<br />\n咁樓主如果可以一開始揀左不上熱門咁冇問題啦"},{"pid":"c58b2989039e34ae80cd2b4a282ca45e92e6b5f7","tid":1659470,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a>"},{"pid":"8d66ca180a7fe97657535eaee5f36df4bad9ece1","tid":1659470,"uid":289259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> IG &ldquo;bye bye starbucks&rdquo; challenge</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659200</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦各位，和理非出嚟啦。"},{"pid":"ab39ba62361ff145b4a7e11fb0a556c5c24b66f3","tid":1659470,"uid":32455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"2972e7aa5047e8a315013c9be49ab60938665ad1","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"f8d72f9776c5e3d886f4ccd10d45c177b8d9e60a","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:55:58.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"59d5eb73462e0168ce73a23dca9d11c26ee852ff","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"30381b5f9157da76e346780220b96d16578bbf12","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"5933f71db934fbfa55b0b0936db8dd6cd6edfea0","tid":1659470,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4d74a3f65c37af633f92d26f83e399c537b7e04","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"d6c04cdf2a7f2e1a80bafe33824b3c6726bd3b0a","tid":1659470,"uid":85179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:12:54.000Z","msg":"微微一辔"},{"pid":"e9c15935fce1a5f28facd2129a7facec6c605dc6","tid":1659470,"uid":85179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>微微一推</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce0b58875cc8584e5ec7639d5451eb9d93d3a715","tid":1659470,"uid":102089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87d75eb831b56efbc725aa19be3f3cfb2ac22369","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:39:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c18a5210bcf6adcb6e326e30e153462186354c30","tid":1659470,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"好on9，熱門本來就唔係單單為某一兩個台而設，加上望遠已經再大幅度增加時事台上到熱門嘅post數量上限，家下接近9成嘅post都係來自時事同政事台，咁仲唔夠要再去扼殺埋其他台上到熱門嘅權利？嗰幾個生活post真係咁阻到你睇行動post？如果要嫌行動post少，點解唔檢討下自己時事台咁多其他post上到熱門？"},{"pid":"b74eb41448d7dc67979bde94e0d1473f044c9c8e","tid":1659470,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"LIHKG 已經一再重申熱門系統會自動依據分台避免熱門內容種類過於單一。<br />\n<br />\n2018 LIHKG: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>熱門系統會自動依據分台避免熱門內容種類過於單一。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D95EEK3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD95EEK3.png&h=f459d2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019 LIHKG:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">系統亦會限制各分台於同一頁中的出現數量，<br />\n以免內容過於單一。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xs5jow4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxs5jow4.png&h=7d732231&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d5152ea6418bb8521de7a10304d95d4ca2eb1b4","tid":1659470,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />needleben啲po會自動opt out<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1c5819de57ca75da8543491b82fbfe7353af36","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c18a5210bcf6adcb6e326e30e153462186354c30","tid":1659470,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"好on9，熱門本來就唔係單單為某一兩個台而設，加上望遠已經再大幅度增加時事台上到熱門嘅post數量上限，家下接近9成嘅post都係來自時事同政事台，咁仲唔夠要再去扼殺埋其他台上到熱門嘅權利？嗰幾個生活post真係咁阻到你睇行動post？如果要嫌行動post少，點解唔檢討下自己時事台咁多其他post上到熱門？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"冇人要扼殺，只係樓主可以自己決定上唔上熱門<br />\n<br />\n有啲post好多人討論但唔想上熱門阻到人咖，例如賭馬post同其他小圈子post。"},{"pid":"dd9d747368e92582aa78c3385e10699944eb8555","tid":1659470,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唯有預設不推文回覆<br />\n同更改熱門準則<br />\n先可以光復連登</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議所有回覆預設係不推文回覆<br />\n以及修改熱門準則</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658904</a><br />\n<br />\n <blockquote>熱門準則<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&bull; 單一用戶 (Unique User) 的觀看次數及停留時間。</span><br />\n&bull; 主題的發表時間：例如在「即時熱門」中，愈新發表的主題將會更容易獲得熱門分數。<br />\n&bull; 不推文回覆數量：例如在一個主題中如有大量會員使用不推文回覆，將會大幅減低熱門分數。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">建議停留時間更改為留言次數(推文回覆)<br />\n單一用戶只計一次</span></span><br />\n相信大部分文宣或者行動Post<br />\n大家推嘅方法都係Click入去 幫手推一下<br />\n而去得到1001嘅討論Post<br />\n一定係有啲活躍User重複留言<br />\n咁樣可以提高有用Post上熱門嘅機會之餘<br />\n更可以拉得到所謂唔重要嘅Post落嚟</blockquote>"},{"pid":"eaf24a92710435960ecdf0a273d097a375fde7a8","tid":1659470,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1c5819de57ca75da8543491b82fbfe7353af36","tid":1659470,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c18a5210bcf6adcb6e326e30e153462186354c30","tid":1659470,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"好on9，熱門本來就唔係單單為某一兩個台而設，加上望遠已經再大幅度增加時事台上到熱門嘅post數量上限，家下接近9成嘅post都係來自時事同政事台，咁仲唔夠要再去扼殺埋其他台上到熱門嘅權利？嗰幾個生活post真係咁阻到你睇行動post？如果要嫌行動post少，點解唔檢討下自己時事台咁多其他post上到熱門？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"冇人要扼殺，只係樓主可以自己決定上唔上熱門<br />\n<br />\n有啲post好多人討論但唔想上熱門阻到人咖，例如賭馬post同其他小圈子post。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"多此一舉，成個熱門絕大多數都係時事post，仲要連幾個生活賭波賭馬post都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你信唔信一出呢個功能就成班連衛兵入人post叫人開返不熱門？<br />\n<br />\n同埋你呢個提議姐係直接叫牙連廢除熱門公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歸根究底只係你哋未有效咁將有用post推上熱門，如果係要加入呢個功能，就應該只限於時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c16a7148c8a11de4cdf8e459fc449b3ce142e8e","tid":1659470,"uid":181659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>入黎幫推行動post啦</strong></span></span><br />\n［重要］做緊個連登小實驗 有興趣入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f760c71a9084c67fe579a531309b1a857c31348f","tid":1659470,"uid":41